Title: Apple Watch - Series 6 Battery Replacement
Body (HTML):
Apple Watch - Series 6 Battery Replacement

 

The Apple Watch - Series 6 has great build quality and design, but it isn't invincible. Since your device is of little use when broken, it's a good idea to bring it to iFixYouri for expert Battery Replacement.

 

Each device has its own lifespan - some devices use higher quality components than others and can last years if properly maintained. Drops, water or liquid, even a jolt can damage your device.

Old or bad batteries can really be frustrating. You might need Battery Replacement if your battery does not hold charge well or charges very slowly or barely at all.

 

After checkout, you'll receive an email confirmation and shipping label. When your phone arrives at our repair center, we do diagnostic tests to determine if any other issues are at play. Outgoing testing ensures that your Apple Watch - Series 6 is fully functional. With the repairs complete, we send you a tracking number and ship your Apple Watch - Series 6 back to you!

 

Send your Apple Watch - Series 6 to iFixYouri via the UPS shipping method of your choosing. Please ship your device in a sturdy, secure box. If you hear it rattling around in the box, add some more padding. Please do not include cases, cables, or accessories. Standard UPS Ground is covered by us, as well as $100 insurance. Faster shipping and extra insurance coverage can be purchased using the drop-down boxes above.

 

A 90-day warranty that covers all but accidental damage comes with every repair.
